PortSystem          1.0

name                xeyes
version             1.0.1
revision            1
categories          x11
platforms           darwin
maintainers         jeremyhu
description         X11 xeyes demo app
long_description    xeyes defies description.

homepage            http://www.x.org
master_sites        http://xorg.freedesktop.org/archive/individual/app/

